6daaf441-203e-4e7f-b0c5-502589b13167.title: Eniola
6daaf441-203e-4e7f-b0c5-502589b13167.text: Well met, fellow adventurer! How can I help you?

options.text: I'd like to access my bank account, please.
I'd like to talk to you about quick payment deals.

d55ca46e-336f-4250-a953-15c086ec4829.title: Eniola
d55ca46e-336f-4250-a953-15c086ec4829.text:
How frightfully rude of me, my dear lady. My name is
Eniola and I work for that most excellent enterprise,
the Bank of Gielinor.

options.text: If you work for the bank, what are you doing here?
I'd like to access my bank account, please.
I'd like to talk to you about quick payment deals.

26db1305-8847-4f04-af52-ddce9815ec19.title: <player>
26db1305-8847-4f04-af52-ddce9815ec19.text: If you work for the bank, what are you doing here?

13469758-3083-4eb1-8c8c-eec26910b1bd.title: Eniola
13469758-3083-4eb1-8c8c-eec26910b1bd.text:
My presence here is the start of a new enterprise of
travelling banks.

137e3d2a-aade-4c93-8c3c-4e0b3db86b01.title: Eniola
137e3d2a-aade-4c93-8c3c-4e0b3db86b01.text:
I, and others like me, will provide you with the
convenience of having banking facilities where they will
be of optimum use to you.

57f2ab5d-badc-440b-b71d-a8b66176158d.title: Eniola
57f2ab5d-badc-440b-b71d-a8b66176158d.text:
The Z.M.I., that is, the Zamorakian Magical Institute,
requested my services upon discovery of this altar. We
at the Bank of Gielinor are a neutral party and are
willing to offer our services regardless of affiliation.

13a2cb99-e0ff-4b1f-a472-c6cbbcd12b21.title: Eniola
13a2cb99-e0ff-4b1f-a472-c6cbbcd12b21.text: So that is why I am here.

72a71df9-bfdd-4632-b00e-20a8ff7b4f89.title: <player>
72a71df9-bfdd-4632-b00e-20a8ff7b4f89.text: Can I access my bank account by speaking to you?

6153c97e-3b8d-4fbc-95dd-4b53175a0b51.title: Eniola
6153c97e-3b8d-4fbc-95dd-4b53175a0b51.text:
However, I must inform you that because the Z.M.I.
are paying for my services, they require anyone not
part of the Institute to pay an access fee to open their
bank account.

05479fe6-6618-4242-8885-0407177733ff.title: Eniola
05479fe6-6618-4242-8885-0407177733ff.text:
But, as our goal as travelling bankers is to make our
customers' lives more convenient, we have accomodated
to your needs. We know you will be busy creating
runes and do not wish to carry money with you. The

4359d468-7435-49de-9b51-26bf2d880fc7.title: Eniola
4359d468-7435-49de-9b51-26bf2d880fc7.text:
charge to open your account is the small amount of
twenty of one type of rune. The type of rune is up to
you.

9573cc7e-af30-4fb2-b99e-c6d2d9b8ff52.title: Eniola
9573cc7e-af30-4fb2-b99e-c6d2d9b8ff52.text:
Would you like to pay the price of twenty runes to
open your bank account?

options.text: Let me open my account and then I'll give you the runes.
No way! I'm not paying to withdraw my own money.

4ef83b8c-213b-46b3-8156-c18f6585e049.title: <player>
4ef83b8c-213b-46b3-8156-c18f6585e049.text: I would like to set up a quick payment deal.

735d9bdb-e0ad-4a2b-9517-772cae8c8584.title: Eniola
735d9bdb-e0ad-4a2b-9517-772cae8c8584.text:
Oh that is most wonderful you know. Let me know
which rune you would like to set up a quick payment
with.

ac1f0ae8-4567-469e-a919-0f7b9956f6b2.title: <player>
ac1f0ae8-4567-469e-a919-0f7b9956f6b2.text:
I don't have the runes on me. Let me open my
account and then I'll give them to you.

45b25888-68fb-4be0-8b6c-de529a192c6f.title: Eniola
45b25888-68fb-4be0-8b6c-de529a192c6f.text:
It's not that I don't trust you, but as the old
adage goes: 'Payment comes before friends.'

162318d6-e964-4b8e-bafc-ec9c3caf16a2.title: <player>
162318d6-e964-4b8e-bafc-ec9c3caf16a2.text:
That's preposterous! I'm not paying runes to withdraw
my own stuff.

4e6e4648-9d45-49ab-acdb-23999cee97c3.title: Eniola
4e6e4648-9d45-49ab-acdb-23999cee97c3.text:
I'm sorry to hear that, madam. If you should
reconsider, because I believe this service offers excellent
value for money, do not hesitate to contact me.
